name: Bob Illutunji
bio: I'm Bob, a passionate dog lover with over 5 years of experience in walking and caring for dogs of all sizes and breeds. I pride myself on providing personalized attention and ensuring that every walk is a fun and safe adventure for your furry friend.
description: Reliable and friendly dog walker dedicated to keeping your pets happy and healthy. I offer individual and group walks, and I can accommodate special needs and requests to ensure your dog gets the best care possible.

name: Jamal Specter
bio: Jamal has been a professional dog walker for over 5 years. He specializes in large breeds and enjoys taking dogs on nature trails.
description: Experienced dog walker with a passion for animals. Provides personalized care and attention.

name: Apollo Ross
bio: An experienced and friendly dog walker with a passion for pets. Apollo has been walking dogs for over 5 years and knows all the best routes in town.
description: Apollo is reliable, caring, and ensures your dog gets the exercise and attention they need. He specializes in walking small to medium-sized dogs and offers personalized care for each pet.

description: Lyra is known for her patience and attention to detail, ensuring each dog gets a tailored experience during their walks. She is experienced with dogs of all sizes and offers both group and solo walks.

description: Jax is known for his punctuality and attention to detail, making sure your dog gets the exercise they need. He specializes in handling energetic dogs and provides tailored walking services.

bio: Booker is a dedicated dog walker with over 3 years of experience in caring for pets. he is known for his gentle approach and his love for all breeds.
